n Dialog eintreten, und erzählt das schillernde und prekäre Miteinander von Wort und Ton in gesungener Kunstmusik neu - als Liebesgeschichte zwischen Hingabe, Verschmelzung, lustvoller Differenz, Abstoßung und Selbstbehauptung.  aThe dazzling, precarious interaction of word and sound as a love story re-narrated: a classification of vocalizations between speaking and singing, from theater recitations to vocalises.  afunded by Kunstuniversität Graz  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mrz 2022) 0aMusic and language. 0aVocal musiczEuropey19th centuryxHistory and criticism. 0aVocal musiczEuropey20th centuryxHistory and criticism. 4aAllgemeine Literaturwissenschaft. 4aGesang. 4aKlang. 4aKunstlied. 4aLied. 4aMusik. 4aMusikwissenschaft. 4aMélodie. 4aSprache. 4aSprachwissenschaft. 4aTheaterdeklamation. 4aTon. 4aVokalise. 4aWort. 7aMUSIC / History & Criticism.2bisacsh  aArt Song.  aGeneral Literature Studies.  aLanguage.  aLinguistics.  aMelody.  aMusic.  aMusicology.  aSinging.  aSong.  aSound.  aTheatre Declamation.  aVocalise.  aWord.2 aKunstuniversität Grazefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2018 Part 2z978311076667708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2018z978311071955008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Studies 2018z9783110603187oZDB-23-DKU40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839443095zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839443095423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839443095/original  a978-3-11-071955-0  DG Plus eBook